n thinks five people have six fingers. Then the eighth person thinks eight','Oliver: I\'m now in grade seven. Jake: What\'s new about grade three? That I don\'t have a mean science teacher. Dave Rich singing about his school blues in the year 1952. The alphabet has 26 letters, but with only nine numbers and a zero, 10 figures.','Oliver is in grade seven. Jake is in third grade. Dave Rich sings about his school blues in the year 1952 '),(62724,149,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/09/10/La Buena Onda - September 10, 2023 at 17:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-09-10 17:00:00',86638720,'2023-09-11 15:49:47',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(62725,144,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/09/09/The Underground - September 9, 2023 at 23:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-09-09 23:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-11 15:49:53',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(62726,145,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/09/10/Visions fugitives - September 10, 2023 at 08:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-09-10 08:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-11 15:49:58',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(62727,149,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/09/10/La Buena Onda - September 10, 2023 at 16:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-09-10 16:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-11 15:50:03',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(62728,148,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/09/10/Clan Na Gael - September 10, 2023 at 13:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-09-10 13:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-11 15:50:09',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(62729,148,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/09/10/Clan Na Gael - September 10, 2023 at 12:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-09-10 12:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-11 15:50:14',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(62730,154,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/09/11/This Night Wounds Time - September 11, 2023 at 01:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-09-11 01:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-11 15:50:26',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(62731,154,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/09/11/This Night Wounds Time - September 11, 2023 at 00:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-09-11 00:00:00',86507648,'2023-09-11 15:50:31',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(62732,154,'https:/