ens and the other on the common lichens of the Great Lakes. Byron wants to know what\'s different about the new book, Macro',NULL,'Big Sis Radio narrator asks you to pledge to silence for a month'),(64841,84,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/02/Blues Around the Block - October 2, 2023 at 20:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-02 20:00:00',86507648,'2023-10-03 02:06:23',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64842,84,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/02/Blues Around the Block - October 2, 2023 at 19:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-02 19:00:00',86638720,'2023-10-03 02:06:24',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64852,86,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/02/The Deep House Project - October 2, 2023 at 22:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-02 22:00:00',86507648,'2023-10-31 05:46:41',NULL,'This week on the Deep House project, Aaron Badgley and the band play a selection of new and older tracks. The first track is by Dabin, who has teamed up with William Black on a song called \"Black in the Cold.\" The band also plays a song by the legendary DJ, Kevin Glasko, \"The Rhythm.\"',NULL,'Aaron Badgley and the band play new and older tracks on Deep House'),(64853,85,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/02/Ripcord Radio - October 2, 2023 at 21:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-02 21:00:00',86507648,'2023-10-03 04:06:18',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64855,1447,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/03/Rainbow Country - October 3, 2023 at 01:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-03 01:00:00',86638720,'2023-10-03 13:49:03',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64856,1447,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/03/Rainbow Country - October 3, 2023 at 00:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-03 00:00:00',86507648,'2023-10-03 13:49:04',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64857,13298,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/03/CFRU Selector - October 3, 2023 at 07:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-03 07:00:00',86507648,'2023-10-03 13:49:44',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(64867,207,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/fjxnuh/Music_w_db_Hawkes_Oct_4_2023_podcastasu27.mp3','2023-10-03 1