10-23 17:00:00',86507648,'2023-10-24 02:06:16',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(67149,86,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/23/The Deep House Project - October 23, 2023 at 22:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-23 22:00:00',86507648,'2023-10-31 05:10:19',NULL,'In this episode of the Deep House project, host Scott Brown and his crew set out to raise money for Silence Sounds, a local organization dedicated to preserving the arts in the community. They invite listeners to pledge $10 a month to the organization for a year. Scott introduces them to the program, which runs every Tuesday at 8pm on the CFRU 93.3 FM station. The program begins with a dance track by a German artist named Levenmankind. The song begins by saying, \"It\'s not about you, and me, so hold on, wait for a day /To feel out where its gonna be.\" The song goes on to say, \"The luck is with Me, the world still stops hidden, I still breathe there\'s something to your eyes / Oh no I know it\'s for so long.\" The artist then says, \"I\'ve got to get you up and move on.\" He tells the listeners that he has a crush on them and he wants to show them how much he wants them to love him. The music starts off with a remix of Milk & Bones\' \"P-Back\" by Blue Hawaii, and then the band Moose and The Scarf comes out with their song \"Won\'t',NULL,'Deep House project host Scott Brown pledges $10 a month to Silence Sounds, a local arts organization'),(67150,85,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/23/Ripcord Radio - October 23, 2023 at 21:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-23 21:00:00',86638720,'2023-10-24 04:06:13',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(67160,87,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/23/Back in the USSR - October 23, 2023 at 23:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-23 23:00:00',86507648,'2023-10-24 06:06:25',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(67161,1447,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/10/24/Rainbow Country - October 24, 2023 at 00:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-10-24 00:00:00',86507648,'2023-10-24 06:07:32',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),(67172,1447,'https://ar