bert\'s favorite labels. The title track is from a new release from Skyphone, called The Spiral itself.',NULL,'The Week\'s Top 10: John Cuthbert\'s New Albums (Sponsor)'),(69029,99,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/11/08/The Stillness & The Dancing - November 8, 2023 at 09:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-11-08 09:00:00',86638720,'2023-11-09 22:11:27',NULL,'This week, the host of The Stillness and The Dancing, Joel Cuthbert, is going through a medical treatment in the city of Toronto. He\'s been spending his weekends back in Guelph, so he\'s recording some music for you. He says that it\'s a weird season for him, and he\'d like to continue to find some fun things to do. So he\'ll be sharing some new music from a friend, the Green Kingdom, who he discovered when he was digging a little deeper into the world of music. The first track on the new album is called \"Gathering Clouds\" and the next track is \"Ether Hymns\", which is coming out on November 11. The title track is about the way in which music and the sounds that form it are brought into being from nothingness, and then drift into the space of the listener. The Green Kingdom is on this album too. They\'re called \"The Green Kingdom\" off of \"Ephemeral Hymns.\" The show goes live on the CFRU 98.3FM station in Guelph.',NULL,'The Stillness and The Dancing host Joel Cuthbert is going through a medical treatment in Toronto. He\'s recording some music for'),(69031,159,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/pppabw/CAREER_-_CareerBuzzCIUTfinalnovember8202364w47.mp3','2023-11-08 18:29:13',85593358,'2023-11-09 21:57:46',NULL,'This week\'s guest on Career Buzz is Matt Moud from Mammoud Machinery, a landscaping equipment distributor in Mississauga, Ontario. Matt\'s father and business partner, Houdra Moud, is the owner of the business. Before starting the business, Matt\'d worked for a variety of corporations, including the Royal Bank, Inc., the BUNZ distribution company, and the Brink\'s security company, among others. He learne