ans in the area. The United Nation\'s humanitarian agency, the UNRWA, has warned that it may soon have to suspend humanitarian operations in the territory due to the scarcity of fuel. An Israeli airstrike on the West Bank town of Janin has killed three people and injured 14. Since the start of the conflict on October 7, Israeli troops have killed more Palestinians than 200 in the West bank.',NULL,NULL),(69375,3686,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/11/17/Volunteer Playlist - November 17, 2023 at 12:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-11-17 12:00:00',86638720,'2023-11-17 22:12:02','2023-11-17 19:07:38','',NULL,NULL),(69376,126,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/11/17/Viejoteca - November 17, 2023 at 14:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-11-17 14:00:00',86638720,'2023-11-17 21:06:46','2023-11-17 21:06:46',NULL,NULL,NULL),(69377,126,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/11/17/Viejoteca - November 17, 2023 at 13:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-11-17 13:00:00',86507648,'2023-11-17 21:06:47','2023-11-17 21:06:47',NULL,NULL,NULL),(69378,182,'https://mcdn.podbean.com/mf/web/dp5dmj/NBR_Nov_16_202382jod.mp3','2023-11-17 22:34:34',152735868,'2023-11-21 20:46:25','2023-11-17 23:05:26','On this episode of Beat the Beat, the guys play a bunch of new music. We hear from a band called Bobozar, a band that reformed recently, and from Australia, with a group called Real Work Mutt. They also hear from Cosmo Vermo, who has a new track called Mid Journey Full Profit. We also learn that Kevin Crump from Turbo LP, AKA Record Detective and Microforms, recommended that they all donate to the station. Then we hear about some of the new bands that have been announced for the show.',NULL,NULL),(69379,127,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/11/17/LiYghTE FM - November 17, 2023 at 16:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','2023-11-17 16:00:00',86507648,'2023-11-17 23:06:46','2023-11-17 23:06:46',NULL,NULL,NULL),(69380,1620,'https://archive.cfru.ca/archive/2023/11/17/Hellfire Radio - November 17, 2023 at 15:00 - CFRU 93.3.mp3','202